d by the expanding radio lobes\nmodel, leaving an accretion disk corona or jets as the possible origins of the\nX-ray emission from this young radio galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 20:14:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-06"}
