ach, and this symmetry gives\ninteresting predictions for hadronic decays involving $b\\to d$ transitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 20:42:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
