to\nmeasure 3-8 GRB/yr, and verify/refute the 2EPLS model with just a few bright\nGRBs. A space-based experiment with an IR channel would make improved\nmeasurements of the self-absorption frequency and physical conditions within\nthe GRB jet. Additional science includes detection of dust evaporation due to\nGRBs, a tool to study progenitor environment dust.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 23:38:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-06"}
