citly include disorder,\nas-prepared Mn$_2$CoAl films are best described as a disordered metal, rather\nthan a spin gapless semiconductor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 23:44:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-06"}
