different from supersymmetry. In\nparticular, the mechanism avoids invocation of super-coordinates or extra\ndimensions for the underlying spacetime manifold.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2019 04:45:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2020 15:53:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 14:51:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-27"}
