$ and DoAr21$c$ are $P_{B}\\sim92.92\\pm0.02$,\n$P_{b}\\sim450.9\\pm3.8$ and $P_{c}\\sim1013.5\\pm25.3$ days, respectively. Since\nthe estimated age of this young star is about 0.4$-$0.8 Myrs, the detected\nBrown Dwarf companion is among the youngest companions observed to date.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2019 15:45:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-16"}
